text: Chayanne es Mi Nombre is the solo album debut from Puerto Rican artist Chayanne, after he left Los Chicos. It was released on RCA Ariola in July 1984. ==Track listing== ==Music videos== #Chayanne es mi Nombre #¿...Y Qué Culpa Tengo Yo? #De Dos en Dos #Chicos Malos ==References== Category:1984 albums
title: Chayanne es mi Nombre
